\": 755}, {\"ngram\": \"security forces\", \"from\": 759, \"to\": 774}, {\"ngram\": \"heavy demand\", \"from\": 779, \"to\": 791}]}, {\"sentence\": \"From Parisians renting out their apartments, to a transit system that has boosted its ticket prices, everyone is looking to make a buck during the Games, including the underworld.\", \"from\": 794, \"to\": 973, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Parisians\", \"from\": 799, \"to\": 808}, {\"ngram\": \"their apartments\", \"from\": 821, \"to\": 837}, {\"ngram\": \"a transit system\", \"from\": 842, \"to\": 858}, {\"ngram\": \"its ticket prices\", \"from\": 876, \"to\": 893}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 895, \"to\": 903}, {\"ngram\": \"a buck\", \"from\": 923, \"to\": 929}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 937, \"to\": 946}, {\"ngram\": \"the underworld\", \"from\": 958, \"to\": 972}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are always ready in this business,\\\" a Parisian dealer told AFP, echoing French leader Emmanuel Macron's judgment this week that his nation is all set for the Games.\", \"from\": 975, \"to\": 1143, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1038, \"end\": 1041, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"score\": 0.9996341223307584, \"rank\": 0.00036601158478812945, \"text\": \"AFP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\"}, {\"begin\": 1065, \"end\": 1080, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Emmanuel Macron\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this business\", \"from\": 999, \"to\": 1012}, {\"ngram\": \"a Parisian dealer\", \"from\": 1015, \"to\": 1032}, {\"ngram\": \"his nation\", \"from\": 1107, \"to\": 1117}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 1133, \"to\": 1142}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There will always be somebody ready, that's how it is when there is money to be made,\\\" said the dealer, on condition of anonymity.\", \"from\": 1145, \"to\": 1276, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"somebody\", \"from\": 1167, \"to\": 1175}, {\"ngram\": \"money\", \"from\": 1214, \"to\": 1219}, {\"ngram\": \"the dealer\", \"from\": 1238, \"to\": 1248}, {\"ngram\": \"condition\", \"from\": 1253, \"to\": 1262}, {\"ngram\": \"anonymity\", \"from\": 1266, \"to\": 1275}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With up to 45,000 security forces policing the streets, experts expect delivery services will see a bump as clients seek to avoid getting busted.\", \"from\": 1278, \"to\": 1423, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"up to 45,000 security forces\", \"from\": 1283, \"to\": 1311}, {\"ngram\": \"the streets\", \"from\": 1321, \"to\": 1332}, {\"ngram\": \"experts\", \"from\": 1334, \"to\": 1341}, {\"ngram\": \"delivery services\", \"from\": 1349, \"to\": 1366}, {\"ngram\": \"a bump\", \"from\": 1376, \"to\": 1382}, {\"ngram\": \"clients\", \"from\": 1386, \"to\": 1393}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In fact, France has already had a boom in messaging app and social media-driven drug deliveries since pandemic lockdowns pushed the trade off the street and onto smartphone screens.\", \"from\": 1425, \"to\": 1606, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1434, \"end\": 1440, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.8830107624861208, \"rank\": 0.1282590587390438, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"fact\", \"from\": 1428, \"to\": 1432}, {\"ngram\": \"a boom\", \"from\": 1457, \"to\": 1463}, {\"ngram\": \"app\", \"from\": 1477, \"to\": 1480}, {\"ngram\": \"social media-driven drug deliveries\", \"from\": 1485, \"to\": 1520}, {\"ngram\": \"pandemic lockdowns\", \"from\": 1527, \"to\": 1545}, {\"ngram\": \"the trade\", \"from\": 1553, \"to\": 1562}, {\"ngram\": \"the street\", \"from\": 1567, \"to\": 1577}, {\"ngram\": \"smartphone screens\", \"from\": 1587, \"to\": 1605}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At the same time, the country has voiced increasing alarm overa flourishing drug trade and deadly violence between rival gangs.\", \"from\": 1608, \"to\": 1735, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the same time\", \"from\": 1611, \"to\": 1624}, {\"ngram\": \"the country\", \"from\": 1626, \"to\": 1637}, {\"ngram\": \"increasing alarm overa\", \"from\": 1649, \"to\": 1671}, {\"ngram\": \"drug trade\", \"from\": 1684, \"to\": 1694}, {\"ngram\": \"deadly violence\", \"from\": 1699, \"to\": 1714}, {\"ngram\": \"rival gangs\", \"from\": 1723, \"to\": 1734}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There is a kind of Uberisation of drug trafficking, with the development of digital offerings on applications like Telegram, or promotional deals,\\\" said criminal attorney Adrien Gabeaud.\", \"from\": 1737, \"to\": 1924, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1853, \"end\": 1861, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Telegraphy\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.414574721500034e-23, \"text\": \"Telegram\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Telegraphy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Telegraphy\"}, {\"begin\": 1909, \"end\": 1915, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeff_Adrien\", \"score\": 0.9999999999354259, \"rank\": 3.1411036919644924e-11, \"text\": \"Adrien\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeff_Adrien\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeff_Adrien\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a kind\", \"from\": 1747, \"to\": 1753}, {\"ngram\": \"Uberisation\", \"from\": 1757, \"to\": 1768}, {\"ngram\": \"drug trafficking\", \"from\": 1772, \"to\": 1788}, {\"ngram\": \"the development