", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Swathes\", \"from\": 2234, \"to\": 2241}, {\"ngram\": \"the festivities\", \"from\": 2287, \"to\": 2302}, {\"ngram\": \"car and pedestrian traffic\", \"from\": 2320, \"to\": 2346}, {\"ngram\": \"the Parisian dealer\", \"from\": 2359, \"to\": 2378}, {\"ngram\": \"the trouble\", \"from\": 2406, \"to\": 2417}, {\"ngram\": \"the events\", \"from\": 2431, \"to\": 2441}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In one exchange between a seller and a customer, seen by AFP, the dealer warns that transactions cannot happen in the open.\", \"from\": 2444, \"to\": 2567, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2501, \"end\": 2504, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"score\": 0.9996341223307584, \"rank\": 0.00036601158478812945, \"text\": \"AFP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"one exchange\", \"from\": 2447, \"to\": 2459}, {\"ngram\": \"a seller\", \"from\": 2468, \"to\": 2476}, {\"ngram\": \"a customer\", \"from\": 2481, \"to\": 2491}, {\"ngram\": \"the dealer\", \"from\": 2506, \"to\": 2516}, {\"ngram\": \"transactions\", \"from\": 2528, \"to\": 2540}, {\"ngram\": \"the open\", \"from\": 2558, \"to\": 2566}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The police are on the lookout,\\\" the message read.\", \"from\": 2569, \"to\": 2619, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The police\", \"from\": 2570, \"to\": 2580}, {\"ngram\": \"the lookout\", \"from\": 2588, \"to\": 2599}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Yet other dealers are sending out messages to assure clients that service will carry on.\", \"from\": 2621, \"to\": 2709, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"other dealers\", \"from\": 2625, \"to\": 2638}, {\"ngram\": \"messages\", \"from\": 2655, \"to\": 2663}, {\"ngram\": \"clients\", \"from\": 2674, \"to\": 2681}, {\"ngram\": \"service\", \"from\": 2687, \"to\": 2694}]}, {\"sentence\": \"One wrote: \\\"I inform you that despite the Olympics, the delivery service will remain the same.\\\"\", \"from\": 2710, \"to\": 2805, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 2748, \"to\": 2760}, {\"ngram\": \"the delivery service\", \"from\": 2762, \"to\": 2782}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is too soon to gauge whether or how much prices could rise, but criminal lawyer David Curiel predicted they are on their way up.\", \"from\": 2807, \"to\": 2938, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2890, \"end\": 2902, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Curiel\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"David Curiel\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Curiel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Curiel\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"how much prices\", \"from\": 2842, \"to\": 2857}, {\"ngram\": \"their way\", \"from\": 2925, \"to\": 2934}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"In Paris a gram of cocaine costs \\u20ac50 (S$73) to \\u20ac60, but now it could probably go up to \\u20ac80 a gram,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 2940, \"to\": 3049, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2944, \"end\": 2949, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999986358, \"rank\": 1.5755139038267587e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"They (dealers) can not wait, for them this is like the sales,\\\" he added, referring to France's government-set promotion periods when shoppers flock to stores.\", \"from\": 3051, \"to\": 3210, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3138, \"end\": 3144, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.88301076